name: Key Lock Box - Box Key Storage Lock for Key Safety & Convenience
description:
Key lock box is a 4-digit password box which helps you to avoid lockout of hosts, brokers, contractors, family members and tenants,


The password lock is ideal for house, emergency entry, vacation home, pet sitters, and office ,The code is easy to change & code can be shared.


The box is made of aluminium alloy lock body, stronger, safer, and effective resistance to violent damage. The device is large hence no need to bring a key when going out, travel more easily, easy to operate

Don't hide your keys underneath your doormat in a flowerpot, keep them safe and secure in the Key Lock Box!


This key lock box is made of aluminium alloy and heavy-duty steel, which can protect the box from hammering, sawing or prying. With 4 resettable digit customized combination offering thousands of different combinations, you don't have to worry about the safety and enjoy the keyle convenience.



feature- Color: Gray- Material: aluminium alloy - Size: 11.5 x 9.5 x 4cmThis key lock box is made of aluminium alloy and heavy-duty steel, which can protect the box from hammering, sawing or prying. Resettable 4 digit customized combination for keyle convenience - Personalized, adjustable combination lock with 4 digit, offering thousands of different combinations.


For indoor and outdoor use; portable lock box is best used for key and acce card storage; And a large capacity room for your keysIt Can Be Wall Mounted or Padlock Mounted Anywhere. Can be mounted on wall by accesories in our package or be hung exactly where you need such as fence, car door handle or house doorknob etc.


1.Keep the weather cover closed to increase weather resistance.


2.We do not recommend use the combination such as "A-A-A-A" which is easy to crack.


3.It is recommended the dials are rotated weekly to keep them moving freely.


4. Shooting light and different displays may cause the color of the item in the picture a little different from the real thing.
